{"tid":115552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老放火】小心縱火疑犯張潤衡又出黎抽水","createTime":"2017-02-10T15:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T16:08:16.000Z","uid":35519,"like":75,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b19855a15405033ae7d4d3124579aed6c383c1","tid":115552,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150703/large/1435914474_6447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150703%2Flarge%2F1435914474_6447.jpg&h=dd8f04a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條仆街上次八仙塵爆已經借人地落難　<br />\n搵埋CCTVB去台灣　一邊食水煎包　一邊做show幫自己宣傳<br />\n<br />\n以佢既性格，今次又可能扮晒過來人身份走出黎<br />\n<br />\n呢條撚人根本極有可能就係當年八仙嶺山火既縱火犯<br />\n<br />\n假如佢又再抽水　懇求大家一定要瘋狂狙擊　要求翻案<br />\n要呢種「殺人放火金腰帶」既人身敗名裂　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0162c79d482afcd2492fbb24ed9d6d3c2a3a4c9","tid":115552,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"41fc8d3417c619ca1cf5aba7e4e45a882dd5426a","tid":115552,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4a02bc3f5c9d83bbcaea8190d5f26eea4f579b","tid":115552,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a069fac5a19460822b633c1ef1e8b42e815b1ae","tid":115552,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0c188f3620f0e0ba9f5d84df962efe9bf2caa2","tid":115552,"uid":77217,"like":0,"dislik